properties.address: Parish Centre, Church Stretton, Shropshire SY6 6DQ
properties.description: Every Saturday morning between 10-12 you will find a 'Warm Welcome' in St Laurence Parish Centre. We provide simple refreshments, good company, newspapers, games and conversation. Our space is accessible, inclusive and inter-generational so please come and join us on a Saturday and make some new friends!
properties.title: A Warm Welcome in Church Stretton
